The Linguist
============

RAILS app to manage strings that are used as lables in your applications.
This application allows you to manage the strings in a bundle, each bundle
has one or more language packs, that represent strings in a particular
language.

Model:

User => One or more Projects
Project => One or more Bundles
Bundle => One or more Language Packs
Language Pack => One or more key/text pairs in a language

